FAQ

Frequently Asked Questions About Pictory AI Video Generator


How does Pictory AI generate videos automatically?

Pictory AI uses advanced AI to instantly transform your text, scripts, or prompts into professional-quality videos. Our technology analyzes your content, then selects the most relevant visuals, background music, and narration from an 18M+ stock library to bring your story to life. You can also choose from realistic AI voices in 29+ languages to match your audience perfectly.

Which is the best AI text-to-video generator?

Pictory is trusted worldwide as one of the best AI text-to-video generators, helping marketers, educators, and creators produce high-quality videos in minutes. Whether you need YouTube explainers, TikTok clips, LinkedIn promos, or training videos, Pictory makes it easy to turn text into scroll-stopping content without editing skills.

What kind of voices does Pictory’s AI video generator provide?

With Pictory, you can choose from realistic AI voiceovers powered by ElevenLabs in over 29 languages and multiple accents. From male and female voices to natural-sounding tones, you’ll always find the right voice to connect with your audience.

Is Pictory beginner-friendly?

Absolutely! Pictory is designed for everyone — from beginners to professional video editors. Our intuitive online editor makes it easy to fine-tune your script, adjust visuals, change fonts, add logos, and instantly preview your video before exporting.

Do I need to download software to use Pictory AI?

No downloads required. Pictory is a fully web-based AI video generator, so it works in your browser on any desktop device . Create and share videos online without installing complex editing software.

Which platforms can I create videos for with Pictory?

Pictory automatically formats your videos for YouTube, TikTok, Instagram, LinkedIn, Facebook, X (Twitter), and more. You can create everything from short-form clips to long-form explainers and marketing campaigns with ease.

Does Pictory support multiple languages?

Yes — Pictory supports 29+ languages for AI voiceovers and can generate videos for global audiences. This makes it a perfect tool for international creators, brands, and educators.

What makes Pictory different from other AI video makers?

Unlike other tools, Pictory combines realistic multilingual AI voices, an 18M+ media library, automatic scene matching, and easy branding customization in one platform. It’s designed to help you create professional, share-ready videos faster and at scale.
